"><div class="media-object-video"><div class="wsj-media-summary clearfix"><div class="strap-container"><h4 class="strap" itemprop="description"></h4></div></div><iframe width="400" height="225" src="https://video-api.wsj.com/api-video/player/v3/iframe.html?guid=52B0CFB0-0E03-4C90-9E19-A15E110CDD96&amp;height=225&amp;width=400&amp;plid=video_amp&amp;chainVideos=true&amp;parentUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fukraine-offensive-weapons-russia-f-16s-biden-administration-mark-milley-263cf9ec&amp;a=a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe><p class="imageCaption">回顾与展望：美国国税局特工加里·沙普利和约瑟夫·齐格勒在宣誓后表示，他们调查亨特·拜登的尝试面临着司法部前所未有的干预。司法部长梅里克·加兰和特拉华州联邦检察官大卫·韦斯会做出回应吗？图片：彭博新闻/盖蒂图片社 综合：马克·凯利<span class="imageCredit">华尔街日报互动版</span></p></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 20 Jul 2023 22:44:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/ukraine-offective-weapons-Russia-f-16s-biden-administration-mark-milley-263cf9ec</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/ukraine-offective-weapons-Russia-f-16s-biden-administration-mark-milley-263cf9ec<author><![CDATA[The Editorial Board]]></author><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>国家/公共安全</category><category>武装部队</category><category>风险新闻</category><category>军事行动</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>国家的</category><category>公安</category><category>武装部队</category><category>风险新闻</category><category>军事行动</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论</category><category>意见</category><category>法蒂瓦过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category></item></channel></rss>